buildout, ", "url": "https://finnhub.io/api/news?id=0a13d54792caacd377f3b710137e17aa0431a56f222dd5c6d847aa8b8be0947c", "source": "Yahoo"}, {"headline": "Google, Meta ruling could be a Tobacco Moment for social media cases", "summary": "The discussion revolves around the \"Miserable Seven\" stocks, which are down double digits from their 52-week highs, and whether it''s a buying opportunity. Kenny advises caution, suggesting that not all stocks are worth buying, and some, like Meta and Google, may face more lawsuits. The recent court ", "url": "https://finnhub.io/api/news?id=fb0932925bf8054f9c3451bc848767a02b6ab36ae82a0acb5daed8587e11da63", "source": "Yahoo"}, {"headline": "Chip stocks react to Google''s AI breakthrough, Henkel acquiring Olaplex", "summary": "Memory chip stocks such as Micron, SanDisk, and Western Digital are down due to Google''s research on new memory compression technology. Olaplex is being sold to Henkel for $1.4 billion, and Navan''s shares are up after reporting an unexpected profit. These companies have seen significant stock moveme", "url": "https://finnhub.io/api/news?id=400a3ba476de88d7baac77293d2bfef51b67e9a59745cd29e91ed1754055f917", "source": "Yahoo"}]');
